description:
Mistress Kara’s Team has been on a roll. Kara has basically chosen every fight for this match. She now choses to have herself wrestling for round 4 against Team captain Cheyenne Jewel. She doesn’t want Cheyenne to go against a weaker opponent and rack up points so Kara is taking on the toughest team member on the Wranglers to try to keep the huge lead they already have
Mistress Kara really does not wanna get fucked today

Going one round with Mistress Kara is futile for Cheyenne. Her only chance she has is to wear Kara down and that just wont happen in one round. Kara comes on strong and fierce

Cheyenne’s team:
Bella Rossi
Paris Lincoln

Rilynn Rae

title: ROUND 4 team captains face off in the most intense wrestling match
